source.name: OAHU Food Establishments
source.description: lists represent all of the permitted Food Establishments.  These include everything from Restaurants, take out, Fast-food, Convenience stores, Mom and Pop Markets, shave ice stands, supermarkets, Mega markets like Costco-Sam’s-Walmart, lunch wagons, food manufacturers, etc
